ter the Conquest it was the commonest male name of all, and not only among the Normans. In the later Middle Ages it was overtaken by   John  , but continued to run second to that name until the 20th century, when the picture became more fragmented."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"William de Minster was born in 1180, in England, United Kingdom. He had at least 1 son with Princess Breanna de Blanch. He died after 1210, in his hometown."},"et":{"1180–Aft 1210":"1180–pärast 1210","1194–1210":"1194–1210","1210–1277":"1210–1277","1180–1210":"1180–1210","Aft 1210":"pärast 1210","1277":"1277","1210":"1210","1194":"1194","1180":"1180","England":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1180–Aft 1210":"1180–1210 jälkeen","1194–1210":"1194–1210","1210–1277":"1210–1277","1180–1210":"1180–1210","Aft 1210":"1210 jälkeen","1277":"1277","1210":"1210","1194":"1194","1180":"1180","England":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1180–Aft 1210":"1180–après 1210","1194–1210":"1194–1210","1210–1277":"1210–1277","1180–1210":"1180–1210","Aft 1210":"après 1210","1277":"1277","1210":"1210","1194":"1194","1180":"1180","England":"Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"William de Minster est né en 1180, à Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Il a eu au moins 1 fils avec Princess Breanna de Blanch. Il est décédé après 1210, dans sa ville natale."},"de":{"1180–Aft 1210":"1180–nach 1210","1194–1210":"1194–1210","1210–1277":"1210–1277","1180–1210":"1180–1210","Aft 1210":"nach 1210","1277":"1277","1210":"1210","1194":"1194","1180":"1180","England":"England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"William de Minster wurde 1180 in England, United Kingdom geboren. Er hatte mit Princess Breanna de Blanch mindestens 1 Sohn. Er starb nach 1210 in seinem Geburtsort."},"ht":{"1180–Aft 1210":"1180–after 1210","1194–1210":"1194–1210","1210–1277":"1210–1277","1180–1210":"1180–1210","Aft 1210":"after 1210","1277":"1277","1210":"1210","1194":"1194","1180":"1180","England":"Angletè, United Kingdom"},"hu":{"1180–Aft 1210":"1180–1210